This beautiful two bedroom air conditioned apartment boasts massive amounts of storage. Furnished with designer brands such as Coco Republic and soft furnishings from Laura Ashley. High end finishes and luxury such as heated towel rails, top quality woollen carpets and plank timber flooring. Large windows give New York style views and floods the apartment with natural light. Suitable for one or two people. Fully equipped kitchen with dishwasher and oven. Bathroom has a washing machine.

Centrally located across the road from Broadway Shopping Centre and one block from the cafés and eateries of Glebe Point Road, close to UTS and Uni of Sydney and only a 5 minute stroll to Central Station, everything you could want is right at your door. Electricity, Hot Water and Air Conditioning are all included in the rent. You only need to set up your account for internet, which is already connected in the building. 

This building offers 24 hour security with a guard at night to ensure piece of mind. The building has coin operated laundry washer and dryer, as well as irons and ironing boards. The building has a large industrial size kitchen on each level with gas burner cook tops, as well as 2 Lounge Rooms, a Games Room, and a Library space for study, plus vending machines for a quick drink or snack. There is also a rooftop desk (currently being upgraded) spanning most of the building, with BBQ's and views of Sydney Harbour (including the bridge for New Years Eve Fireworks).

- All bedrooms have generous storage and clothing wardrobes
- Lounge space with TV

- Each bedroom has its own desk with chair for study
- Air conditioner, electricity and hot water included
- Building has a wide variety of common areas to enjoy, including library, pool/games rooms and vending machines
- A pool and gym in the building will be available in the future
